# RealTimeFlowMap - Live Metric Stream Chart

RealTimeFlowMap provides a clean visualization of live numeric values for dashboards and metric feeds.

## Features
- Scrollable line chart  
- Real-time updates  
- Minimal setup  

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/29_RealTimeFlowMap.git
cd 29_RealTimeFlowMap
python visualize.py
